This is what it looks like when a board of directors wants to demonstrate its ability to act in difficult times.
Because WestLB, which is hurting, is still under a lot of pressure.
It is not only the European Commission but also the Federal Financial Supervisory Authority that has, only recently, made it clear to the government of the Land of North Rhine-Westphalia that time is running out in the search for a future solution.
