In the long term, a splitting of the WestLB could take place, which is obviously not desirable here.
This is also what is mentioned in the letter from the existing management committee: in any case, a 'global solution' for the institution would be sought.
How all this will be put into the same basket with the merger of certain entities with the Deta-Bank remains to be seen.
